echanisms that prioritize equitable outcomes over aggregate accuracy. Potential impact includes more robust deployment of FL in high-stakes domains such as hiring, lending, and clinical decision support, where fairness drift must be actively suppressed. Furthermore, by enhancing fairness without requiring full data centralization or universal client homogeneity, FairAlign strengthens both ethical integrity and participant trust in federated ecosystems.",
